<div class="row">
    <div class="thumbnail">


        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card mb-3 " style="width:500px">
                    {{#if user.photo}}
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/uploads/{{user.photo.filename}}" alt="...">
                    {{else}}
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/assets/img/empty.jpg" alt="...">
                    {{/if}}

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-header text-center">

                        Account Information</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2> 접속 계정 : {{user.email}}</h2>
                        <hr>


                        <h4>이름 : {{user.name}}</h4>
                        <br>

                        <h4>닉네임 : {{user.nick}}</h4>
                        <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">게시판에서 사용자에게 노출되는 닉네임입니다.</small>
                        <hr>

                        <p>현재 페이지는 접속중인 계정에 대한 기본적인 정보를 제공하며 이를 수정하는 것 또한 가능합니다. &nbsp;

                        </p>
                        <button type="button" class="btn" id="editbutton">정보 수정</button>
                        <button  type="button" data-id="{{user._id}}" class="btn btn-danger btn-delete" role="button" id="btn_delete" name="btn_delete">삭제</button>




                        <div class="container" id="editor">

                            <form method="post" action="/update" class="form-horizontal" enctype="multipart/form-data">

                                <input type="hidden" name="user_id" class="form-control" id="user_id" value="{{user._id}}">


                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="user_email">email</label>
                                    <div class="form-label-group">
                                        <input name="user_email" class="form-control" id="user_email" value="{{user.email}}">
                                    </div>
                                    <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">계정은 꼭 바꿔주셔야 합니다.</small>

                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="example-date-input">name</label>
                                    <div class="form-label-group">
                                        <input name="user_name" class="form-control" type="name" placeholder="name" id="user_name" />
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="user_email">nickname</label>
                                    <div class="form-label-group">
                                        <input name="user_nick" class="form-control" type="nick" placeholder="nick" id="user_nick" />
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="example-date-input">password</label>
                                    <div class="form-label-group">
                                        <input name="user_password" class="form-control" type="password" placeholder="password" id="user_password" />
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="inputEmail3" class="col-sm-2 control-label">사진</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                                        <input type="file" name="file" class="form-control-file" id="exampleInputFile" aria-describedby="fileHelp">
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-submit" id="btn-edit" name="btn-edit">수정</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </form>

                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer small text-muted">Information page</div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>



<br><br>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-header text-center">
                About the medicine
                <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">즐겨찾기 또는 관심을 표한 약품을 관리할 수 있습니다.</small>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <canvas id="myBarChart" width="100%" height="50"></canvas>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer small text-muted">Medicines</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<p class="small text-center text-muted my-5">
    <em>More functions coming soon...</em>
</p>
